Description.zhCN: 将主巢幼虫变异为各种异虫单位。
Description.enUS: Mutate Hive Larva into various zerg units.

Tooltip.zhCN:
基础工作单位。用于采集晶体矿和高能瓦斯。可以变异为建筑。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Basic work unit. Used to collect crystal minerals and high-energy gas. Can be mutated into buildings.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
强大迅捷的肉搏型生物。一只母巢幼虫可变异为两只噬兽。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
A powerful and swift melee-type creature. One Brood Larva can mutate into two Eating Beasts.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
提供补给。
提高本方单位数量上限。

无法攻击。
Tooltip.enUS:
Provide supplies.
Increase the maximum number of own units.

Cannot attack.

Tooltip.zhCN:
致命的远程攻击单位。能够使用狂暴技能。可以变异为裂地者。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Deadly ranged attack unit. Able to use rage skills. Can mutate into Earthbreaker.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
能够孵化大量蝗虫进行攻击的消耗单位。

蝗虫可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
A consumable unit that can hatch a large number of locusts to attack.

Locust can attack ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
可怕的飞行生物。能够利用弹射攻击连续伤害多个目标。可以变异为母巢守卫与吞噬者。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Terrifying flying creatures. Able to use projectile attacks to damage multiple targets in a row. Can mutate into Brood Guard and devourer.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
恐怖的虫群施法单位。可以使用恶毒菌群、微晶态装甲云和寄生感染技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Terrifying insect swarm spellcasting unit. Can use Vicious Bacteria, Microcrystalline Armor Cloud, and Parasitic Infection skills.

Can target the ground.
Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.zhCN:
强大的突击单位。潜地后能快速恢复生命值。能够使用埋地冲锋和应激甲壳技能。可以变异为梦魇虫

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Powerful assault unit. HP can be quickly restored after burrowing. Ability to use Buried Charge and Stress Carapace skills. Can mutate into Nightmare Bug

and can attack the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
强大的重型攻击猛兽，可造成范围伤害。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
A powerful heavy attack beast that can cause area damage.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
致命的自毁式飞行单位。一只母巢幼虫可变异为两只弑杀蜂。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Deadly self-destructing flying unit. One Brood Larva can mutate into two Killer Wasps.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
致命的自毁式飞行单位。一只母巢幼虫可变异为两只弑杀蜂。

可以对地和对空。

受到宏伟尖塔加成：
造价与建造时间降低50%
Tooltip.enUS:
Deadly self-destructing flying unit. One Brood Larva can mutate into two Killer Wasps.

Can be used against ground and air.

Bonus from Magnificent Spire:
The cost and construction time are reduced by 50 %

Tooltip.zhCN:
擅长对空的强大飞行生物。能够变异为利维坦巢母。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
A powerful flying creature that is good at anti-aircraft. Can mutate into Leviathan Hive Mother.

Can be used against ground and air.

Name.zhCN: 变异为恶性畸变体

Tooltip.zhCN:
坚固的重型近战单位。能够使用冲锋技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
A solid heavy melee unit. Able to use charge skills.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
飞行的施法者，战地的控场大师。可使用绑架、黑暗虫群和寄生弹技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Flying spellcaster, master of battlefield control. Can use Kidnapping, Dark Swarm and Parasitic Bomb skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
大型飞行作战生物。能够发射蝗虫与弑杀蜂来攻击目标。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Large flying combat creature. Can launch Locusts and Killer Bees to attack targets.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
大威力自毁型单位。爆炸时能够造成范围的伤害。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
A powerful self-destructive unit. Can cause a range of damage when exploded.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
重型远程火炮单位。可以使用梦魇轰炸技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Heavy long-range artillery unit. Can use the Nightmare Bombing skill.

Can target the ground.

Name.zhCN: 变异为巨型湮灭虫

Tooltip.zhCN:
致命的大威力自毁型单位。爆炸时能够造成大范围的伤害。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
A deadly and powerful self-destructing unit. It can cause a wide range of damage when it explodes.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
恐怖的反地面伏击单位。可对火力线上的所有敌方单位造成伤害。

可以对地。
必须潜地后才能发动攻击。
Tooltip.enUS:
Terrifying anti-ground ambush unit. Can cause damage to all enemy units in the line of fire.

Can target the ground.
You must burrow before launching an attack.
Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Name.zhCN: 变异为阿尔法王虫

Tooltip.zhCN: 使王虫获得武器与耐久强化，并可运输单位。
Tooltip.enUS: Allows Overlord to gain weapons and durability enhancements, and can transport units.

Tooltip.zhCN:
高级空中侦察单位。 可以使用污染技能。

侦测单位
Tooltip.enUS:
Advanced aerial reconnaissance unit. Can use pollution skills.

Detection unit

Name.zhCN: 变异为母巢吞噬者

Tooltip.zhCN:
非常强大的对空飞行单位。攻击能够削弱敌人。

可以对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Very powerful anti-air flying unit. Attacks weaken enemies.

Can be empty.

Tooltip.zhCN:
能够在远距离攻击地面单位的强大巨型飞行生物。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
A powerful giant flying creature capable of attacking ground units at long range.

Can target the ground.

Name.zhCN: 变异为利维坦巢母

Tooltip.zhCN:
大型飞行作战生物。能够投射母巢寄生虫与弑杀蜂来攻击目标。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Large flying combat creature. Able to project Brood Parasites and Killer Wasps onto targets.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
世末降临。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
The end of the world is coming.

Can target the ground.
